{"tid":2151820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁晃維精煉重溫去年811 警暴","createTime":"2020-08-11T14:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:09:30.000Z","uid":306528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3d3464daaf67e14f41d369a2d7f80152b11491","tid":2151820,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"選舉主任DQ我嘅其中一個理由，係話我將香港同中國之間嘅關係描繪成「戰爭狀態」。黃智華想知答案嘅，不如睇吓一年前嘅今日發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n呢一晚，可謂顛覆咗香港人對警暴嘅想像，黑警泯滅人性，濫用致命武力，犯下多項國際標準下嘅戰爭罪行：<br />\n<br />\n1. 葵芳，室內使用催淚彈，企圖以化學武器毒殺平民<br />\n2. 銅鑼灣，黑警偽裝成抗爭者，製造衝突再暴力拘捕市民，甚至喺鏡頭前插贓嫁禍<br />\n3. 太古，近距離行刑式掃射正在撒離嘅示威者，再將多人推落扶手電梯<br />\n4. 尖沙咀，惡意描頭射擊，射盲參與急救工作嘅少女。<br />\n<br />\n黑警喺811嘅暴行馨竹難書，施暴嘅手段亦令大家睇清楚佢哋早已唔係執法者，而係政權嘅冷血屠夫。中國打壓示威活動唔單止要令我哋噤聲，更加係要將我哋趕絕殺盡，令二十多年嚟拒絕妥協，頑強抵抗嘅香港民族消亡殆盡。<br />\n<br />\n有黑警問：「你哋真係咁憎我哋？」<br />\n<br />\n係，剩係811一晚都夠我憎你哋一世。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n梁晃維 Fergus Leung<br />\n中西區區議員（觀龍) <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n休戚與共 長風破浪<br />\n📷Instagram | <a href=\"http://instagram.com/fergus.lfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffergus.lfw&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=4dce86fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/fergus.lfw</a><br />\n🐤Twitter | <a href=\"http://twitter.com/FergusLeung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFergusLeung&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=f9932590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/FergusLeung</a>"},{"pid":"2d926df9f9be0dea7fb18059ac3aaa572ed18230","tid":2151820,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以陪伴到112個人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57b406cdf799b869f51313766c7a200830eefdf